  "title": "ReFi Roundup #35: Orbs everywhere, Return Protocol, ReFi Jobs & ReFi events ğŸ—º",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-35",
  "html": "<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://c.tenor.com/bL2mbsCaVfAAAAAC/orbs-toy-story.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"498\" height=\"278\"></figure><p>Happy Monday ReFi Nation!</p><p>It's another beautiful week in regenerative finance. There is so much to explore. So many orbs, so many events and such little time. How do you make sense of it all?</p><p>I'm very grateful to the wonderful community of content creators who have come around the ReFi movement over the last few months. With <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZGkZaxI-9E\">This Week in ReFi</a>, <a href=\"https://web3climate.substack.com/\">Venturing in ReFi</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats\">ThoughtFloats</a>, <a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/tag/decarbonized/\">deCarbonized</a> and <a href=\"https://refijobs.com/blog\">ReFi Jobs</a> â€”there is so much great content to choose from.</p><p>This week we're going to give an overview of what else is out there in the space and ask our readers one vital question: </p><p><em>âœ¨ What is the most useful direction we can take with our weekly newsletter? âœ¨</em></p><h2 id=\"shape-the-future-of-refi-roundup-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Shape the future of ReFi Roundup ğŸ‘‡ğŸ½</h2><p>We began this newsletter in January 2022 to help people stay up to date with all the amazing happenings in the regenerative finance space. We want to engage with our community about where to go next.</p><p>Respond to our 2-min survey and drop your email if you'd like a surprise.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://tally.so/r/nGxP7z\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Take the 2-min survey</a></div><hr><h2 id=\"return-protocol-on-refi-podcast\">Return Protocol on ReFi Podcast</h2><p>Check out the latest episode with Kieran and Andrew from Return Protocol. This project is a much needed investment in making climate action EASY and SOCIAL. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">What if you could easily calculate on-chain emissions in a fun, community based wayğŸ¤¯<br><br>Welcome to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReturnProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReturnProtocol</a>! In Ep.8 of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReFiPodcast</a> we had the opportunity to sit down and dive deep into new tides of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a><br><br>LetsğŸ§µit<br>ğŸ‘‚<a href=\"https://t.co/9UN94FUji8\">https://t.co/9UN94FUji8</a><br>ğŸ‘€<a href=\"https://t.co/KH63KMRHOB\">https://t.co/KH63KMRHOB</a><br>(1/8)</p>&mdash; ReFi Podcast (@ReFiPodcast) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast/status/1572738590224035841?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 22, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-community-content\">ReFi Community Content</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"find-something-new-subscribe-like-and-share\">Find something new, subscribe, like and share...</h3></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Fortnightly on-chain carbon stats for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ToucanProtocol</a>:<br><br>- Total Traded: $751k<br>- Total Retired: 2779 tonnes<br><br>ğŸ—ï¸ Read the full issue of deCarbonized on <a href=\"https://t.co/htVS8JNqJT\">https://t.co/htVS8JNqJT</a><br><br>.. or stay here for the summarized version <a href=\"https://t.co/4HIQMvWKTe\">pic.twitter.com/4HIQMvWKTe</a></p>&mdash; Toucan (@ToucanProtocol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol/status/1572196833757401090?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 20, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"toucans-decarbonized-cdr-frameworks-scrutiny-refis-expanding-horizons\">Toucan's deCarbonized: CDR frameworks scrutiny &amp; ReFi's expanding horizons...</h2><p>Check out this week's piece by Vaisakh covering the much-needed scrutiny of Europe's CDR frameworks published in <a href=\"https://www.ecologic.eu/sites/default/files/publication/2022/50084-ECF-CDR-report-web.pdf\">a report by Ecologic Institute</a>, with some key highlights below:</p><ul><li>The frameworks of most EU member states mistakenly equate CDR with emission reductions</li><li>Nature sinks need to play a more significant role in most national frameworks when compared to technology-based solutions</li><li>Ideally, CDR should rank much lower. There are issues of cost, land use and biodiversity issues among others</li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/decarbonized-30/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the newsletter</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">1/ ğŸ™ï¸ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ownereconomy?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ownereconomy</a> releases a new episode of The Ownership Economy podcast featuring <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gregory_landua?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gregory_landua</a> (of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@regen_network</a>) discussing the link between the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/permaculture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#permaculture</a> movement and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>, natural capital assets, and the future of Regen Network.<a href=\"https://t.co/qhpy845pS6\">https://t.co/qhpy845pS6</a></p>&mdash; ThoughtFloats (@ThoughtFloats) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats/status/1573761439969398784?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 24, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"refi-weekly-rewind-%E2%80%94-sep-24-%F0%9F%8E%90\">ReFi Weekly Rewind â€” Sep 24 ğŸ</h2><p>This Twitter thread from our friends at Thought Floats is jam packed with everything you need to know about ReFi this week. Seriously, everything.</p><p>Go ahead, read it. It's good stuff. Some highlights:</p><ul><li>New weekly newsletter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats/status/1573761442716610560?s=20&amp;t=ZzZPlJ-hLvGIO4lOzrvpSA\">Brave New Earth</a> from Brave New DAO</li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AtlantisDAO1/status/1572606950109773825?s=20&amp;t=ZzZPlJ-hLvGIO4lOzrvpSA\">Atlantis partners with Mercy Corps Ventures</a> to launch another environmental and social impact project in rural India</li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats/status/1573761474811437056?s=20&amp;t=ZzZPlJ-hLvGIO4lOzrvpSA\">WEF launches Crypto Sustainability Coalition</a> with Flowcarbon, Toucan Protocol, Climate Collective, Plastiks, Nori and Klima DAO</li><li>Owocki releases <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7QftdMGQuo\">an episode on Filecoin Green with Alan Ransil</a></li><li>Sequestr.io launches an invite-only beta of <a href=\"https://t.co/GDg24mPBJ3\">it's on-chain carbon marketplace</a></li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats/status/1573761439969398784?s&#x3D;20&amp;t&#x3D;D5etiovtjcMUDie44mcVGQ\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the full rewind</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NZGkZaxI-9E?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Gold Standard Steps Up - This Week In ReFi - Episode 20 9-23-2022\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"this-week-in-refi-is-back-%F0%9F%8D%8C\">This Week in ReFi is BACK... Â ğŸŒ</h2><p>with a golden banana. ğŸ¤£</p><p>If you haven't tuned in to Slaptain and Rez's weekly recap of the carbon market happenings in ReFi, please do. It's an absolute joyâ€”as always. They also cover broader DeFi and climate tech market to give a bigger picture of the space.</p><p>Slaptain is the former community manager at KlimaDAO who noticed that Solid World gigabrain Rez had a gold mine of information in his noggin that needed to be shared with the world. In this week's episode they cover:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/NZGkZaxI-9E?t=266\">Gold Standard's Tokenized Carbon Consultation</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZGkZaxI-9E&amp;t=1808s\">Klima's HFC-23 cleanup</a></li><li>GR15 wrap-up highlighting <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MRV1O1\">MRV101</a> and <a href=\"https://gitcoin.co/grants/4024/refi-dao-season-one\">ReFi DAO</a> grants</li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/NZGkZaxI-9E?t=1750\">Ethereum Merge retrospective</a></li><li>EU limits subsidies for <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZGkZaxI-9E&amp;t=1970s\">wood pellets as a 'renewable' energy source</a></li><li>Binance <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZGkZaxI-9E&amp;t=2220s\">BUSD move</a></li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#x3D;NZGkZaxI-9E\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Watch the episode</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-25.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1658\" height=\"1516\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-25.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-25.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/image-25.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-25.png 1658w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"web3-climate-news-with-venturing-in-refi-%F0%9F%9A%80\">Web3 Climate news with Venturing in ReFi ğŸš€</h2><p>Our friends at Aera Force are building a Venture DAO focused on web3 climate projects. They also do a great bi-weekly newsletter. It's condensed and leans towards the investor side of the equation.</p><p>They provide a nice overview of the GR15 round, explain Gitcoin and quadratic funding as well as highlighting a few select grants from the climate solutions round.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://web3climate.substack.com/p/venturing-in-refi-22\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the newsletter</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-accent\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"%E2%80%9Dthe-greatest-weapon-against-stress-is-our-ability-to-choose-one-thought-over-another%E2%80%9D\">â€The greatest weapon against stress is our ability to choose one thought over another.â€</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"-william-james\">- William James</h3></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-light\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-jobs\">ReFi Jobs</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"top-jobs-at-leading-regenerative-finance-ventures\">Top jobs at leading regenerative finance ventures.</h3><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View more</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/676314-senior-web3-developer-solid-world-dao\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-26.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1428\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-26.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-26.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-26.png 1428w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></fig