34.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-34.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-34.png 1116w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/6308bac0e33a780010245bf1\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-35.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1124\" height=\"738\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-35.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-35.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-35.png 1124w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-36.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1124\" height=\"770\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-36.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-36.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-36.png 1124w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://carbon-forward.com/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-30.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1694\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-30.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-30.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/image-30.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-30.png 1694w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refispring.com/events\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View more events</a></div><hr><h2 id=\"thank-you\">Thank you!</h2><p>I hope you have another awesome week exploring the most exciting opportunity in human history. </p><p><em>What is the most useful direction we can take with our weekly newsletter? ğŸ‘‡ğŸ½</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://tally.so/r/nGxP7z\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Submit our reader survey</a></div>",
